high_descs: Walk to the left kitchen sink behind you.
Grab a bottle from the sink.
Walk back and locate the bottom-left count drawer under the left sink.
Place the bottle in that drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move a bottle from the counter to the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Grab the white lotion bottle with a brown pump.
Turn around and back up towards the bath tub, then turn around to the sink again.
Open the right cabinet door under the sink and place the lotion inside.
anns.task_desc: Place the lotion on the sink underneath the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink countertop.
Pick up the bottle of lotion.
Turn to face the cabinet underneath the sink.
Put the bottle of lotion underneath the sink in the second cabinet from the left.
anns.task_desc: Put the bottle of lotion underneath the sink.
